---
title: Middle Eastern Veggie Pearl Couscous with Feta Yoghurt & Parsley
description: Grab a bowl and the largest spoon you own because you’ll want to eat as much of this nutritious veggie couscous as possible. Enjoy root veggies like pumpkin, parsnip and beetroot roasted and spiced, which add both a pop of colour and flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W16_NZ_edit__Main_high-b3717a7b.jpg
